reviews.text: Clean station and the cabs are right outside the station and always available.
Staff are rude and unhelpful. Worst customer service i have ever encountered, they look at you like you have interupted their day when you ask for help.
Not very busy but useless staff. Rarely anyone at the help point. Very annoying.

Very rude staff. Asked twice for help in two different occasions (  2different member of the stuff)  for the same problem: I was carrying a bike and the big gate didn't work so I asked if for help multiple times and they just didn't move from their chair , just looked at me and tell me to tap again the oyster :/ 
I ends up going through the small gate , as no support was provide and got stuck with my bike and the stuff member was more annoyed as he had to come and open manually. Sorry if I disturb you when you were playing with your phone!!!
A very pleasant station, not very busy, clean and with friendly staff onsite.
